high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wooden dresser on the right.
Pick up the black clock to the right of the sets of keys on the dresser.
Turn around, head to the wall and walk to the small nightstand next to the bed on the right.
Turn on the small lamp on the left corner of the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a clock by the light of a small lamp.

Pick up the alarm clock to the right of the keys, on the dresser.
Turn to your left and go past the bed, then turn right and go to the night stand at the end of the room.
Turn on the lamp on the on the back, right corner of the night stand.
